version_description:
- Now Shop In-store and save $ on your everyday grocery items. Try it out by going to the In-Store tab in Shop
- Bug fixes and updates to make MyPoints even better

- Earn Points for watching fun, fresh content in the brand new Watch tab
- Check on your Daily Goal and keep track of your Current Streak or complete your To-Do List to earn bonus Points in the new Daily Bonus tab
- Bug fixes and optimizations to make your daily MyPoints experience even better
